name: OFC Obrakorp Fighting Coliseum
summary: Obrakorp Fighting Coliseum is an immersive fighting and fitness game that will immerse you into a dystopian future held with an iron fist by Jim Obram and his robots. Thrown into arenas around the world, you will have to use the best (and worst) of late 23rd century technology. Blades, gauntlets, cannons, lasers, deadly combos, ultimate cyber-techniques, sodas, ...
